    "Conversely, for sequences that exceed this size, we truncate the length of the source code.",
    "Deep Feature Generation ModuleThe initial step in this module involves generating embedding vectors for each token within the feature sequences.",
    "Subsequently, the pre-trained CodeT5+ is used to extract the deep features from the embedding vectors.",
    "Considering the high expense of training CodeT5+,(IA) 3 vectors are injected into both the multi-head attention layer and the FFN to enhance efficiency.",
